Royal Court Official Emoni: Why, what is it, what is it,
what is ittt~!?

Royal Court Official Emoni: Ah, you all! D-did you come all
the way here to chase after me!?

Royal Court Official Emoni: I-if you lay a hand on me, Lady
Caron won't stay silent--

Priestess Sophia: We came to investigate the ruins on
behalf of the Magic Academy's request.
Priestess Sophia: Hehe, Emoni-san, why are you here?

Royal Court Official Emoni: I am here for the ruins
investigation as a court official! I-it's true, I assure
you!

Priestess Sophia: I see... It seems that Emoni-san has a
close relationship with Lady Caron, doesn't she?
Clea: Well then, we will go for the investigation.
Royal Court Official Emoni: That's impossible!

Royal Court Official Emoni: This ruins has a special
structure. It's likely that without the right number of
people, you won't be able to reach the top floor.
Clea: I see... That's troublesome, isn't it?

Royal Court Official Emoni: I, as a court official, am
willing to assist! Our interests align when it comes to
investigating the Tower of Betrayal.

Royal Court Official Emoni: Haa...!? Where am I, huh, why
am I outside the tower...?
Thief Nora: I carried it out!

Royal Court Official Emoni: Ohohoho! I know that you all
have allied with the Prince's faction!

Royal Court Official Emoni: The time will come when we will
fight seriously! So be prepared, as I won't hold back!

Royal Court Official Emoni: W-Well, I do appreciate that
you helped me, at least.

Royal Court Official Emoni: Ohohoho, let's meet again on
another occasion!
Mage Relm: Somehow, she's not a person I can hate.

Priestess Sophia: When the time comes to fight seriously...
at that moment...
Clea: Let's go report to Prince Rex.
